{
  "page": "Jeyne Swann",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\"><img alt=\"House Swann.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/94/House_Swann.svg/50px-House_Swann.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/94/House_Swann.svg/75px-House_Swann.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/94/House_Swann.svg/100px-House_Swann.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Jeyne Swann</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\"><img alt=\"House Swann.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/94/House_Swann.svg/50px-House_Swann.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"55\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/94/House_Swann.svg/75px-House_Swann.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/94/House_Swann.svg/100px-House_Swann.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\"></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\">House Swann</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Dornish_Marches\" title=\"Dornish Marches\">Marcher</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Jeyne Swann</b> was a member of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Swann\" title=\"House Swann\">House Swann</a> during the reign of King <a href=\"/index.php/Aerys_II_Targaryen\" title=\"Aerys II Targaryen\">Aerys II Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> It is currently unknown if Jeyne is still alive in the main series. Her relation to Lord <a href=\"/index.php/Gulian_Swann\" title=\"Gulian Swann\">Gulian Swann</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Stonehelm\" title=\"Stonehelm\">Stonehelm</a>, the current head of the House, is also unknown.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Swann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Ser <a href=\"/index.php/Barristan_Selmy\" title=\"Barristan Selmy\">Barristan Selmy</a> rescued Lady Jeyne and her <a href=\"/index.php/Septa\" title=\"Septa\">septa</a> from the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingswood_Brotherhood\" title=\"Kingswood Brotherhood\">Kingswood Brotherhood</a> defeating the <a href=\"/index.php/Smiling_Knight\" title=\"Smiling Knight\">Smiling Knight</a> and killing <a href=\"/index.php/Simon_Toyne\" title=\"Simon Toyne\">Simon Toyne</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Jeyne_Swann&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos67.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_67\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 67\">Chapter 67</a>, Jaime VIII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403192852\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.060 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.235 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 427/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 10424/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 4816/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 252/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 807/5000000 bytes\nLua time usage: 0.160/7.000 seconds\nLua virtual size: 6.5 MB/50 MB\nLua estimated memory usage: 0 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%  226.317      1 -total\n 97.02%  219.574      1 Template:Infobox_character\n 96.18%  217.681      1 Template:Infobox\n 11.60%   26.247     12 Template:Infobox_value\n  3.46%    7.822      3 Template:Infobox_label\n  2.22%    5.029      2 Template:Ref\n  1.36%    3.074      2 Template:Ref/core\n  0.67%    1.510      1 Template:References\n  0.39%    0.891      1 Template:Main_other\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved in parser cache with key westeros_awoiaftest-mw_:pcache:idhash:4897-0!canonical and timestamp 20260403192852 and revision id 317937\n -->\n",
